43:38.291 --> 43:40.041
-You really like to drink.
-Pardon?

43:40.125 --> 43:41.083
You like to drink.

43:41.166 --> 43:43.583
-It's great.
-But the thing is

43:44.791 --> 43:46.291
I eat a lot when I drink.

43:47.000 --> 43:49.250
-Drinking is all about the food.
-Right?

43:49.333 --> 43:52.375
Yes, of course.
I never want to drink when I'm full.

43:53.083 --> 43:55.416
I only drink when I'm hungry.
Never when I'm full.

43:56.500 --> 43:58.250
I just really love this vibe.

43:58.875 --> 44:02.083
When I drink, I care a great deal

44:02.166 --> 44:04.208
about the lighting and music.

44:05.708 --> 44:09.666
-That's what all late bloomers say.
-Are you calling me an amateur?

44:10.541 --> 44:14.250
I have control over them
when I drink at home, but not here.

44:14.333 --> 44:16.958
I never drink when I'm sad.

44:17.041 --> 44:18.083
That's good.

44:18.166 --> 44:19.666
You see, drinking…

44:20.416 --> 44:22.541
It makes me happier on good days.

44:22.625 --> 44:24.708
And it's like a friend on bad days.

44:25.333 --> 44:28.541
But when I'm drinking alone,
I only drink beer or wine.

44:29.458 --> 44:30.375
Soju is…

44:32.708 --> 44:35.708
-I feel pitiful if I drink soju alone.
-It looks lame.

44:35.791 --> 44:36.916
Yes, exactly!

44:37.416 --> 44:39.083
But surprisingly,

44:40.000 --> 44:43.375
when I have someone to drink soju with,

44:44.416 --> 44:46.125
I just love that interaction.

44:47.000 --> 44:50.166
When I think about the things in life

44:50.250 --> 44:53.916
that make me happy,

44:54.000 --> 44:59.583
I feel the happiest
when I see my loved ones happy.

45:00.083 --> 45:03.791
I'm happiest when I'm having good food

45:04.625 --> 45:08.833
over nice drinks with the people I love
and sharing experiences with them.

45:08.916 --> 45:10.416
That's the right way to drink.

45:10.500 --> 45:11.833
-You think so?
-Yes.

45:11.916 --> 45:13.041
That's great.

45:41.916 --> 45:46.250
I don't crave for wine or beer
when I drink with people.

45:46.333 --> 45:50.708
But when you drink soju with people,
it helps you bond at a deeper level.

45:55.750 --> 45:59.166
DAESUN

46:12.750 --> 46:16.083
JOEUNDAY

46:17.208 --> 46:19.541
But I can't drink soju by myself.

46:20.583 --> 46:24.791
Soju has this power to…

46:25.375 --> 46:26.666
It bonds people.

46:26.750 --> 46:28.291
It brings people together.

46:28.375 --> 46:32.333
It breaks the ice and helps you
befriend even those you barely know.

46:32.416 --> 46:33.333
Totally.

46:33.416 --> 46:36.750
But I can't drink it by myself.

46:38.791 --> 46:39.708
It makes sense.

