48:06.125 --> 48:06.958
Mom.

48:07.916 --> 48:09.666
-Hey.
-You're at my place.

48:10.666 --> 48:12.666
-Yeah.
-What are you doing?

48:13.208 --> 48:15.000
How many bottles have you had?

48:15.500 --> 48:17.208
We only had three bottles.

48:17.291 --> 48:18.500
Look, here.

48:20.833 --> 48:23.083
-What did you have for dinner?
-Yeah.

48:24.250 --> 48:26.375
-What?
-What did you have for dinner?

48:27.541 --> 48:31.583
Your uncle took us out for hoe.

48:31.666 --> 48:33.666
I see. Are you sleeping there tonight?

48:34.666 --> 48:35.500
Yeah.

48:36.375 --> 48:37.750
Okay.

48:40.166 --> 48:41.333
Come meet my mom.

48:41.416 --> 48:43.875
-Mom.
-Yes?

48:44.708 --> 48:45.666
Meet seonbaenim.

48:45.750 --> 48:47.458
-Hello.
-Hello.

48:48.166 --> 48:50.708
-Nice to meet you.
-This is my mom.

48:50.791 --> 48:53.000
Let's grab a drink together next time.

48:53.083 --> 48:55.958
-Mom, he lives in our neighborhood.
-My gosh!

48:56.458 --> 48:57.958
I'll invite you to my place.

48:58.041 --> 49:00.250
-She'll be…
-Come over sometime.

49:00.333 --> 49:01.791
I'll make makgeolli.

49:02.833 --> 49:05.083
-Thank you for inviting me.
-She drinks a lot.

49:05.166 --> 49:06.250
That's okay.

49:06.875 --> 49:08.500
All right, Mom. Good night.

49:09.125 --> 49:10.416
Bye.

49:17.250 --> 49:19.083
You have to invite us over.

49:20.083 --> 49:22.208
-Sure thing.
-We'll be there.

49:22.291 --> 49:23.541
Yes, of course!

49:24.291 --> 49:26.666
-I'll pour you one.
-Let me pour you one.

49:48.541 --> 49:50.666
I love a fun night
of drinking with friends

49:50.750 --> 49:53.750
where everyone's having a great time.

49:54.458 --> 49:57.333
But if I drink when I'm stressed or sad,

49:57.416 --> 50:00.291
it makes me feel even sadder.

50:00.916 --> 50:03.208
I once drank when I got my heart broken.

50:03.791 --> 50:05.833
Someone broke your heart? Crazy bastard!

50:05.916 --> 50:07.583
Come on.

50:08.333 --> 50:09.583
No one would believe you.

50:11.541 --> 50:12.791
My goodness.

50:12.875 --> 50:15.041
-But I was…
-Some guys are just too spoiled.

50:18.166 --> 50:20.333
It happens, you know.

50:21.541 --> 50:24.416
But I think listing excuses
as to why you want to break up

50:24.500 --> 50:26.333
is such a cowardly thing to do.

50:27.166 --> 50:31.000
You can end things because
you don't love the person as much anymore.

50:31.083 --> 50:32.625
I don't know.

50:32.708 --> 50:34.541
Looking back now, I think

50:34.625 --> 50:37.208
it's good to experience
many things in life, good or bad.
